These are all

1700
01:10:42,800 --> 01:10:44,433
the things I like about you.

1701
01:10:44,433 --> 01:10:45,667
Do you want to come home with me, sis?

1702
01:10:58,167 --> 01:11:00,533
Sincerity truly moves everything.

1703
01:11:02,767 --> 01:11:04,467
Even cooking a meal can be so heartwarming.

1704
01:11:04,467 --> 01:11:06,067
You two haven't stopped smiling.

1705
01:11:06,067 --> 01:11:07,400
You deserve this.

1706
01:11:08,033 --> 01:11:09,600
They are happy.

1707
01:11:09,600 --> 01:11:11,167
You sly old fox.

1708
01:11:11,167 --> 01:11:11,800
I'm a 30-year-old.

1709
01:11:11,800 --> 01:11:13,333
Why am I so excited about a head pat?

1710
01:11:13,333 --> 01:11:15,233
Actually, I'm a bit shy.

1711
01:11:15,233 --> 01:11:17,000
He was really scared, Xiao Hu.

1712
01:11:17,000 --> 01:11:18,567
You don't know what happened.

1713
01:11:18,567 --> 01:11:19,633
This extra isn't good.

1714
01:11:19,633 --> 01:11:20,500
Almost messed up the scene.

1715
01:11:20,500 --> 01:11:23,067
It far exceeded my expectations.

1716
01:11:23,067 --> 01:11:24,367
You're the coolest mom.

1717
01:11:24,367 --> 01:11:26,733
I'm the most girlish mom.

1718
01:11:26,733 --> 01:11:28,267
If this is called being a coward,

1719
01:11:28,267 --> 01:11:29,500
then there are no brave people left.

1720
01:11:29,500 --> 01:11:31,167
Very good.

1721
01:11:32,100 --> 01:11:34,600
Class monitor, leave last.

1722
01:11:34,600 --> 01:11:35,433
Because I feel in my heart

1723
01:11:35,433 --> 01:11:35,800
I will definitely feel

1724
01:11:35,800 --> 01:11:37,300
that we will meet again.

1725
01:11:39,033 --> 01:11:41,067
My most unforgettable moment is

1726
01:11:41,367 --> 01:11:42,700
when I opened the door and saw her.

1727
01:11:46,500 --> 01:11:48,533
The moment I always think of is

1728
01:11:48,533 --> 01:11:49,767
Then Liang Tian went to them

1729
01:11:50,300 --> 01:11:51,667
and exchanged a song.

1730
01:11:52,000 --> 01:11:53,733
I think that was a beautiful moment.

1731
01:11:53,733 --> 01:11:54,800
My first reaction was confusion.

1732
01:11:54,800 --> 01:11:56,033
Luo Luo was confused.

1733
01:11:58,167 --> 01:11:58,733
Luo Luo was stunned.

1734
01:12:00,333 --> 01:12:03,400
The things we shouted on the mountain that day

1735
01:12:03,400 --> 01:12:05,000
As long as I make a promise,

1736
01:12:05,000 --> 01:12:06,500
I will definitely keep it.
